posts.subject: Covid vaccine
posts.body:
Something to be worried about? Or more chicken little?

Have long argued that all "vaccine" production should take place in the patient. Triggered by exposure to the positively dead pathogen. That way, you bypass many levels of mischief and stupid. No "extra ingredients" either.

I get the flu shot every year but have always wondered if those suppliers can be trusted.

posts.body:
>>f03f106c-275c-40e4-9845-861968280195

You had better hope that Biden played by the rules. Because many are listening to both sides - could be persuaded either way. But if it comes out in court, not the media circus, that Biden and company cheated - well, there's just no limit to where this could take us.

This isn't a fucking game. Consequences will be real. You only need an almost insignificant portion of your population to switch from "accommodating" to punishing. The remainder will sit it out and wait for the winner. "Be cowed or be dead".

Scores aplenty remain to be settled. This isn't really about Trump. He might be the catalyst, but he didn't create this conflict. 

Trump is under no obligation to accept cheating. And if he wilts under pressure, his supporters will feel betrayed. They might go after HIM.

Of course, there is always a chance Trump did lose. If that comes out and is believed, his supporters will probably accept it with a grace no Democrat is capable of.

Politics is a contest of will. Consider the implications. Be careful when you don't understand your opposition. 

Republicans do have fear. Democrats don't.

posts.subject: Are you yet at the point where you wonder.....
posts.body:
"has anything the government or media claimed proved true".

Or, "how long has this been going on?"

Wonder if we'll ever see a ruthlessly accurate news replacement ever take hold in this country? Wokesters and fakers need not apply (they wouldn't last anyway).

Would be refreshing to hear "WE investigated this situation thoroughly and are now more confused than when we started. Clearly, these people are working hard to hide the truth". 

No narrative - just an unflinching willingness to call out potential liars. And once you get that reputation with the public - it's difficult to shake. Advertisers will flee.

Is this a death wish for the media as we know it? Yes. And I hope all those fired live in pain and poverty forevermore. Fuck you Fox. You started this. Now the communist news beats you at your own game. It's a dirty bird which dirties it's own nest.
